
*	msg.ex2  --  msg example #2

*	Application-specified values:
*	<Subroutine Name>     CHARACTER*(*)

*	msg fast-reference ID for message:
	INTEGER IDE1
	SAVE IDE1       !Keep it static, or it does no good.

	DATA IDE1 / 0 /   !Always initialize fast-reference IDs to zero.


*	Here's a CPU-efficient way to display a message which might become disabled:
	CALL Message( '<Subroutine Name>-E1  This is a pedagogical error message', 1, IDE1 )

